Comment: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:29.98,OP1,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the first time you have faced a friend's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the way of the Shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:37.21,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,520)}The white past\N The secret feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The white past, the secret feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What bloodlust.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks nothing like he used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,His Chakra repelled my attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Could Naruto's seal have been broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The seal is merely about to break
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Chakra of the Kyuubi is escaping, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately the seal is not completely broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Zabuza?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're both busy people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's against your style,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think it's about time we stopped playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we settle this once\Nand for all with the next move?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you possibly do in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi, show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't withstand his power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabuza-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't defeat this boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabuza-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You... from that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I killed your dear friend, you can't kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that energy of yours go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't defeat me with that kind of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't he someone special to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there someone special in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect someone special to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make that person's dream a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They pity and don't finish off the enemy they ought to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They let them survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To me that isn't compassion or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How it feels to not be needed by anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,To live day to day without a dream.\NThe pain of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabuza-san has no use for a weak Shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You took away my reason for existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to serve a guy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He takes money from thugs to do bad things!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that no brows the only person special to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago I had other people special to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They were my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born in the Land of Water,\Nin a small village heavy with snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents worked on a small farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We were very poor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but my parents seemed to be satisfied with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They were loving parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was old enough to understand things,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My father, he killed my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he tried to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,After the experience of the ceaseless civil war,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,people with Kekkei Genkai were\Nhated and feared in the Land of Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kekkei Genkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They are special powers or Jutsu\Npassed on through certain clans,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,from parent to child or from grandparent to grandchild.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of their special powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,those of the clans were exploited in all sorts of battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, all Kekkei Genkai were feared as harbingers of disaster and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,After the war was over,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they decided to hide their special powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:10:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone knew of their secret only death would await them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that boy went through much suffering as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The greater your power, the more you were feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother had a Kekkei Genkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She kept it secret from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She hoped that for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she must have thought that\Nthey could have a simple life forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why him too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That hurts, Mommy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Haku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Father had discovered our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I had killed my own father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And that moment, what I thought of myself was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,no, that is what I had to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then knew that it was the most painful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The most... painful thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that my existence didn't matter to anyone else in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be the best Ninja in the village and make everyone respect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone comes along and\Naccepts you for who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,no one could be more important\Nto you than that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though Zabuza-san knew I was from a clan with a Kekkei Genkai,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,he took me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.23,0:13:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My power that everyone hated...\NHe wanted it, needed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Brats like you won't be needed by anyone and die like dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the same eyes as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be needed by someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to give everything for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on your power belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Haku, bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to leave the Land of Water as of tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'll be back in this land some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I will rule over this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What I need isn't consolation,\N encouragement or empty words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What I really need is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:15:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your weapon, Zabuza-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep me by you as a mere tool\Nthat heeds your every word.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize, Zabuza-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't good enough to be\Nthe tool you were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:46.11,TLnote,,0,0,0,,(Ninja art summoning: Earth style, Tracking Fang Technique)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninpou Kuchiyose: Doton Tsuiga no Jutsu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:16:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have absolutely no idea where I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know exactly where you are and what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You are completely in my hands now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What, just what's going on out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't use your eyes or ears, simply use your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what happens when you're closing your eyes in the midst of fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Summoning Jutsu specialized for pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I deliberately shed my own blood to stop your attacks both times for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:17:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your weapons have a thick scent of\Nmy blood on them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are my cute Ninja Dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And their sense of smell is unmatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who was playing into my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The fog has lifted already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And your future is... death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of your bluffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing you can do in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your death is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You were too full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too ambitious for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You failed to assassinate the Mizukage and to pull off a coup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You left the service with few men under you and became a rogue ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon after, your name reached Konoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You needed to raise funds to strike back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And you needed to hide from the Tracking Unit's pursuit and retaliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that about the reason why you hired yourself out to scum like Gato?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really believe I've managed\Nto survive with just the Sharingan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's something I didn't copy, a Jutsu of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To enlighten you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:47.79,TLnote,,0,0,0,,(Raikiri: Lightning Cutter)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Raikiri
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,His hand is visibly overflowing with Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You are too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tazuna-san, the man you are trying to assassinate is the symbol of courage in this land!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The bridge he is building is the hope of this land!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And your ambitions will sacrifice countless lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't how a Shinobi is supposed to behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have always fought for my own ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And that will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huuuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your future is... death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you hesitating for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What you said is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a weapon?\NJust a tool for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How can you call him special to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, what is wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabuza-san counts on me even if I'm worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He made me feel needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I've lost my usefulness that justified my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabuza-san no longer needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I am now asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, hurry.
